column5: Can you believe it?  They sent my income tax return form back to me!  In response to question # 4, "Do you have any dependants?" I replied - "2.1 million illegal immigrants, 1.1 million crack heads, 4.4 million unemployable people, 901 thousand people in over 85 prisons, and 650 idiots in Parliament.  Apparently, this was NOT an acceptable answer.  Who the hell did I miss?
You missed all you old farts collecting pensions, while all us younguns are slaving away everyday

NOW NOW.....we old farts payed into those pension plans....unlike Cliff's dependants......  Speaking of having them send it back to you.....I had that happen one year because the form I downloaded off the IRS website had the wrong date at the top of the page....it was the year before's form that was EXACTLY the same as the current year except it said 2007 instead of 2008....
you know what im feeling that way and im going to take my chances and fill it in that way and see what happens.  Peter
Cliff, I wanna see the check you get in the mail with a return like that!
Cliff you forgot all of those fish you feed!
